    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be roadworthy. The exterior shows substantial wear, including several large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Mechanically, the engine starts but runs roughly and frequently stalls, likely needing a major overhaul. The transmission is also showing signs of failure, with significant delays and slipping when shifting. Inside, the cabin has seen better days; the upholstery is torn in multiple places, and several interior components are cracked or missing. It is being sold as-is, primarily for parts or as a major restoration project for an experienced mechanic.",
