      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom-equivalent condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its original purchase. The exterior features a mirror-like finish with zero paint chips, scratches, or swirl marks, complemented by wheels that are entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the interior is pristine; the premium leather remains supple and taut, and the cabin is free of any odors or wear. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule by certified master technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, and the vehicle drives with the same tightness and precision it possessed on day one. With exceptionally low mileage and a documented history of careful ownership, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a piece of engineering that feels and looks virtually untouched.",
